gw.api.util

Class PCSequenceUtilKeyRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.util.PCSequenceUtilKeyRegistry

  • public class PCSequenceUtilKeyRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the registry for any and all keys used when invoking the method @link gw.api.system.database.SequenceUtil.next(long, String) that generates unique IDs for the database, and therefore relies on unique sequence keys in order to work correctly i.e. without collisions. Therefore if you intend to invoke the method SequenceUtil.next(long initialValue, String sequenceKey) with a sequenceKey that is not yet part of this registry, please add it to this registry as a "public static final String" before using it
